{"type": "article", "id": 22332, "title": "从清洁工到女明星，她拍摄了许多女性的化妆间", "description": "我们姑且可以称之为“化妆间摄影”，但这也是一种女性群像。", "date": "2016-02-16T19:00:00Z", "super_tag": "", "tags": [{"id": 153, "name": "摄影"}, {"id": 23445, "name": "女性摄影"}, {"id": 7319, "name": "摄影师"}, {"id": 23446, "name": "化妆间"}], "category": 17, "author": 37534, "comment_count": 1, "praise_count": 62, "image": "img/article/article_show/201607021053387weRFgzpWDKlftUG.jpg", "contents": "\n\n<p>让我们先把时钟拨回到 1978 年。</p>\n<p>迈阿密电影节的无聊晚宴结束后后，Maxi Cohen 去到了女化妆间，她想要休整一下。她是一位女摄影师，同时也是一位导演。“我被眼前的戏剧性画面震动了。女星们穿着奢华的礼服，化妆间到处堆着散乱的珠宝。女人们在反复描着她们的眉毛，往鼻子上扑着粉，涂着嘴唇。”Maxi 随即拿起手中的相机，拍下了第一张照片。</p>\n<p>接下来的二十年，Maxi 一直留意着女化妆间。从清洁工到女明星，从医院到秀场，Maxi 在工作之余不断地拍着照片，<a href=\"http://www.itsnicethat.com/articles/maxi-cohen-ladies-rooms-around-the-world-120216\">并完成了名为 “Ladies’ Rooms Around the World” 的一系列作品。</a></p>\n<div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160702105334i0FdfZ8wraTKupqP.jpg\" alt=\"\" class=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.66712707\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\n<figcaption class=\"\"><div style=\"text-align: center;\">Maxi Cohen 的摄影作品</div></figcaption></figure></div>\n<div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160702105334hQBz1kalebLg5ZiP.jpg\" alt=\"\" class=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.66712707\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\n<figcaption class=\"\"><div style=\"text-align: center;\">Golden Globe Awards LA 2000</div></figcaption></figure></div>\n<div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160702105335w7LcXBnZElsgDSrJ.jpg\" alt=\"\" class=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.66712707\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\n<figcaption class=\"\"><div style=\"text-align: center;\">East Side Air Terminal NYC 1981</div></figcaption></figure></div>\n<div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160702105335ZJrQ9BRvP4Vn7kAO.jpg\" alt=\"\" class=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.66712707\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\n<figcaption class=\"\"><div style=\"text-align: center;\">Black and Blue Ball 2002</div></figcaption></figure></div>\n<div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160702105336lPdfkMZoLe0biThW.jpg\" alt=\"\" class=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.66712707\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\n<figcaption class=\"\"><div style=\"text-align: center;\">Casino Deauville France 1978</div></figcaption></figure></div>\n<div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/201607021053369Pmeid1XWNRlQTKv.jpg\" alt=\"\" class=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.66712707\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\n<figcaption class=\"\"><div style=\"text-align: center;\">Area NYC 1985</div></figcaption></figure></div>\n<div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160702105337YPabWog1DkHpAF7h.jpg\" alt=\"\" class=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.66712707\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\n<figcaption class=\"\"><div style=\"text-align: center;\">Rainbow Room NYC 1984</div></figcaption></figure></div>\n<div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/201607021053376lWijFoexSnPBMUN.jpg\" alt=\"\" class=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.66712707\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\n<figcaption class=\"\"><div style=\"text-align: center;\">Miami Film Festival 1998</div></figcaption></figure></div>\n<p>Maxi 的足迹遍布澳大利亚内陆、赞比亚迪斯科厅、戛纳电影节后台、里约热内卢的桑巴舞学校等等。“这些照片都出于我的个人经验，我尽量保持它们在风格上的统一” Maxi 说。</p>\n<p>对许多女性来说，化妆间是一个安全的避风港。不论她们是在化妆间里补妆还是发呆，都是一种私人的仪式。Maxi 的作品也带有着强烈的个人风格和倾向。</p>\n<p><a href=\"http://www.maxicohenstudio.com\">在 Maxi 的个人网站上</a>，你还可以看到她的电影作品、摄影作品和艺术装置。</p>\n<p class=\"\"><br></p>\n<p>题图来源：<a href=\"http://cms.qdaily.com/manager/articles/22332/medium_editor\">itsnicethat</a></p>\n\n"}